# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LServices Recruitment Hub — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your credentials
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Gmail SMTP — used to send quiz results to Service@LServicesTheCompany.com
#
# GMAIL_USER   → the Gmail address you want to SEND FROM (e.g. yourname@gmail.com)
# GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD → a Gmail App Password (NOT your regular password)
#
# How to create a Gmail App Password (takes 2 minutes):
#   1. Go to myaccount.google.com → Security → 2-Step Verification (enable if off)
#   2. Go to myaccount.google.com → Security → App passwords
#   3. Select "Mail" + "Other (Custom name)" → type "LServices Hub" → Generate
#   4. Copy the 16-character password shown and paste it below
#
GMAIL_USER=your-gmail@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
